metadata.name: $FROG #1
metadata.description: 🐸 $FROG 🐸 FrogInuCoin is one of the newest examples of the “Non-fungible token” in Ethereum and was the inspiration for the ERC-721 standard that powers most digital arts and collectibles.  🐸 $FROG 🐸 FrogInuCoin are a collection 4.444 small 🐸 $FROG 🐸 creatures trying to escape the tyrannical rule of the Jungle.  No two are exactly alike, and each one of them can be officially owned by a single person on the Ethereum blockchain.
